{
  "video_id": "pMYYx_im5QI",
  "title": "Daniel Suarez: The kill decision shouldn't belong to a robot",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12691.0,
      "end_time": 15849.0,
      "text": "I write fiction sci-fi thrillers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15849.0,
      "end_time": 18420.0,
      "text": "so if I say \"killer robots,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18420.0,
      "end_time": 20403.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d probably think something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20403.0,
      "end_time": 22958.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m actually not here to talk about fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22958.0,
      "end_time": 25906.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here to talk about very real killer robots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25906.0,
      "end_time": 29280.0,
      "text": "autonomous combat drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29280.0,
      "end_time": 32655.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not referring to Predator and Reaper drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32655.0,
      "end_time": 35915.0,
      "text": "which have a human making targeting decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35915.0,
      "end_time": 39440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about fully autonomous robotic weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39440.0,
      "end_time": 41697.0,
      "text": "that make lethal decisions about human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41698.0,
      "end_time": 44115.0,
      "text": "all on their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44115.0,
      "end_time": 48115.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s actually a technical term for this: lethal autonomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48115.0,
      "end_time": 50971.0,
      "text": "Now, lethally autonomous killer robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50971.0,
      "end_time": 54400.0,
      "text": "would take many forms -- flying, driving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54400.0,
      "end_time": 56786.0,
      "text": "or just lying in wait."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56786.0,
      "end_time": 59895.0,
      "text": "And actually, they&#39;re very quickly becoming a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59895.0,
      "end_time": 62379.0,
      "text": "These are two automatic sniper stations"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62379.0,
      "end_time": 66515.0,
      "text": "currently deployed in the DMZ between North and South Korea."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66516.0,
      "end_time": 68687.0,
      "text": "Both of these machines are capable of automatically"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68687.0,
      "end_time": 72211.0,
      "text": "identifying a human target and firing on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72211.0,
      "end_time": 76535.0,
      "text": "the one on the left at a distance of over a kilometer."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76535.0,
      "end_time": 80124.0,
      "text": "Now, in both cases, there&#39;s still a human in the loop"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80124.0,
      "end_time": 82496.0,
      "text": "to make that lethal firing decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82496.0,
      "end_time": 87908.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not a technological requirement. It&#39;s a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87909.0,
      "end_time": 91200.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s that choice that I want to focus on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91200.0,
      "end_time": 93643.0,
      "text": "because as we migrate lethal decision-making"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93643.0,
      "end_time": 96752.0,
      "text": "from humans to software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96752.0,
      "end_time": 100228.0,
      "text": "we risk not only taking the humanity out of war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100228.0,
      "end_time": 103753.0,
      "text": "but also changing our social landscape entirely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103754.0,
      "end_time": 105978.0,
      "text": "far from the battlefield."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105978.0,
      "end_time": 110487.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because the way humans resolve conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110487.0,
      "end_time": 112220.0,
      "text": "shapes our social landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112220.0,
      "end_time": 114853.0,
      "text": "And this has always been the case, throughout history."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114853.0,
      "end_time": 117514.0,
      "text": "For example, these were state-of-the-art weapons systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117514.0,
      "end_time": 119592.0,
      "text": "in 1400 A.D."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119593.0,
      "end_time": 122737.0,
      "text": "Now they were both very expensive to build and maintain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122737.0,
      "end_time": 125976.0,
      "text": "but with these you could dominate the populace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125977.0,
      "end_time": 129866.0,
      "text": "and the distribution of political power in feudal society reflected that."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129866.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132553.0,
      "text": "Power was focused at the very top."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132553.0,
      "end_time": 136810.0,
      "text": "And what changed? Technological innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136810.0,
      "end_time": 137952.0,
      "text": "Gunpowder, cannon."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137952.0,
      "end_time": 141769.0,
      "text": "And pretty soon, armor and castles were obsolete,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141769.0,
      "end_time": 144302.0,
      "text": "and it mattered less who you brought to the battlefield"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144302.0,
      "end_time": 148810.0,
      "text": "versus how many people you brought to the battlefield."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148810.0,
      "end_time": 151719.0,
      "text": "And as armies grew in size, the nation-state arose"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151719.0,
      "end_time": 155399.0,
      "text": "as a political and logistical requirement of defense."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155399.0,
      "end_time": 157775.0,
      "text": "And as leaders had to rely on more of their populace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157775.0,
      "end_time": 159608.0,
      "text": "they began to share power."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159608.0,
      "end_time": 162207.0,
      "text": "Representative government began to form."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162207.0,
      "end_time": 165495.0,
      "text": "So again, the tools we use to resolve conflict"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165495.0,
      "end_time": 168799.0,
      "text": "shape our social landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168799.0,
      "end_time": 172863.0,
      "text": "Autonomous robotic weapons are such a tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172863.0,
      "end_time": 178310.0,
      "text": "except that, by requiring very few people to go to war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 178310.0,
      "end_time": 182871.0,
      "text": "they risk re-centralizing power into very few hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182871.0,
      "end_time": 189386.0,
      "text": "possibly reversing a five-century trend toward democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189386.0,
      "end_time": 191143.0,
      "text": "Now, I think, knowing this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191143.0,
      "end_time": 195495.0,
      "text": "we can take decisive steps to preserve our democratic institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195495.0,
      "end_time": 199474.0,
      "text": "to do what humans do best, which is adapt."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 199474.0,
      "end_time": 201478.0,
      "text": "But time is a factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201479.0,
      "end_time": 204330.0,
      "text": "Seventy nations are developing remotely-piloted"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204330.0,
      "end_time": 206487.0,
      "text": "combat drones of their own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206487.0,
      "end_time": 209790.0,
      "text": "and as you&#39;ll see, remotely-piloted combat drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209800.0,
      "end_time": 213552.0,
      "text": "are the precursors to autonomous robotic weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213552.0,
      "end_time": 216319.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because once you&#39;ve deployed remotely-piloted drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216319.0,
      "end_time": 219702.0,
      "text": "there are three powerful factors pushing decision-making"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219703.0,
      "end_time": 224303.0,
      "text": "away from humans and on to the weapon platform itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 224303.0,
      "end_time": 229562.0,
      "text": "The first of these is the deluge of video that drones produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 229562.0,
      "end_time": 233415.0,
      "text": "For example, in 2004, the U.S. drone fleet produced"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 233415.0,
      "end_time": 238727.0,
      "text": "a grand total of 71 hours of video surveillance for analysis."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238727.0,
      "end_time": 243226.0,
      "text": "By 2011, this had gone up to 300,000 hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 243226.0,
      "end_time": 246375.0,
      "text": "outstripping human ability to review it all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 246375.0,
      "end_time": 250390.0,
      "text": "but even that number is about to go up drastically."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 250390.0,
      "end_time": 252613.0,
      "text": "The Pentagon&#39;s Gorgon Stare and Argus programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 252614.0,
      "end_time": 255778.0,
      "text": "will put up to 65 independently operated camera eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 255778.0,
      "end_time": 257815.0,
      "text": "on each drone platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 257815.0,
      "end_time": 261118.0,
      "text": "and this would vastly outstrip human ability to review it."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 261119.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263279.0,
      "text": "And that means visual intelligence software will need"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 263279.0,
      "end_time": 267327.0,
      "text": "to scan it for items of interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 267327.0,
      "end_time": 268675.0,
      "text": "And that means very soon"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 268675.0,
      "end_time": 271422.0,
      "text": "drones will tell humans what to look at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 271422.0,
      "end_time": 273919.0,
      "text": "not the other way around."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 273919.0,
      "end_time": 276392.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a second powerful incentive pushing"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276392.0,
      "end_time": 279775.0,
      "text": "decision-making away from humans and onto machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279775.0,
      "end_time": 282647.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s electromagnetic jamming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 282647.0,
      "end_time": 284883.0,
      "text": "severing the connection between the drone"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 284883.0,
      "end_time": 287697.0,
      "text": "and its operator."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 287697.0,
      "end_time": 290315.0,
      "text": "Now we saw an example of this in 2011"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 290315.0,
      "end_time": 293271.0,
      "text": "when an American RQ-170 Sentinel drone"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 293271.0,
      "end_time": 297578.0,
      "text": "got a bit confused over Iran due to a GPS spoofing attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 297578.0,
      "end_time": 302691.0,
      "text": "but any remotely-piloted drone is susceptible to this type of attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302692.0,
      "end_time": 304744.0,
      "text": "and that means drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304744.0,
      "end_time": 308364.0,
      "text": "will have to shoulder more decision-making."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308364.0,
      "end_time": 311407.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll know their mission objective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311407.0,
      "end_time": 316252.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ll react to new circumstances without human guidance."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 316252.0,
      "end_time": 318833.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll ignore external radio signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 318833.0,
      "end_time": 321163.0,
      "text": "and send very few of their own."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 321163.0,
      "end_time": 323169.0,
      "text": "Which brings us to, really, the third"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 323169.0,
      "end_time": 327310.0,
      "text": "and most powerful incentive pushing decision-making"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 327310.0,
      "end_time": 330373.0,
      "text": "away from humans and onto weapons:"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 330373.0,
      "end_time": 333666.0,
      "text": "plausible deniability."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 333666.0,
      "end_time": 336553.0,
      "text": "Now we live in a global economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 336553.0,
      "end_time": 340887.0,
      "text": "High-tech manufacturing is occurring on most continents."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 340887.0,
      "end_time": 343801.0,
      "text": "Cyber espionage is spiriting away advanced designs"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 343801.0,
      "end_time": 345687.0,
      "text": "to parts unknown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 345687.0,
      "end_time": 347701.0,
      "text": "and in that environment, it is very likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 347701.0,
      "end_time": 352435.0,
      "text": "that a successful drone design will be knocked off in contract factories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 352435.0,
      "end_time": 354605.0,
      "text": "proliferate in the gray market."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 354605.0,
      "end_time": 357650.0,
      "text": "And in that situation, sifting through the wreckage"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 357650.0,
      "end_time": 360250.0,
      "text": "of a suicide drone attack, it will be very difficult to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360250.0,
      "end_time": 364424.0,
      "text": "who sent that weapon."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364425.0,
      "end_time": 367225.0,
      "text": "This raises the very real possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 367225.0,
      "end_time": 370160.0,
      "text": "of anonymous war."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 370160.0,
      "end_time": 372774.0,
      "text": "This could tilt the geopolitical balance on its head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 372774.0,
      "end_time": 376265.0,
      "text": "make it very difficult for a nation to turn its firepower"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 376265.0,
      "end_time": 379113.0,
      "text": "against an attacker, and that could shift the balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 379113.0,
      "end_time": 382877.0,
      "text": "in the 21st century away from defense and toward offense."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 382877.0,
      "end_time": 386100.0,
      "text": "It could make military action a viable option"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 386100.0,
      "end_time": 388289.0,
      "text": "not just for small nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 388289.0,
      "end_time": 390834.0,
      "text": "but criminal organizations, private enterprise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 390834.0,
      "end_time": 393313.0,
      "text": "even powerful individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 393313.0,
      "end_time": 396640.0,
      "text": "It could create a landscape of rival warlords"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 396641.0,
      "end_time": 400321.0,
      "text": "undermining rule of law and civil society."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 400321.0,
      "end_time": 403937.0,
      "text": "Now if responsibility and transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 403937.0,
      "end_time": 406321.0,
      "text": "are two of the cornerstones of representative government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 406321.0,
      "end_time": 410641.0,
      "text": "autonomous robotic weapons could undermine both."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 410641.0,
      "end_time": 412187.0,
      "text": "Now you might be thinking that"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 412187.0,
      "end_time": 414433.0,
      "text": "citizens of high-tech nations"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 414433.0,
      "end_time": 417135.0,
      "text": "would have the advantage in any robotic war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 417136.0,
      "end_time": 420769.0,
      "text": "that citizens of those nations would be less vulnerable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 420769.0,
      "end_time": 425570.0,
      "text": "particularly against developing nations."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 425570.0,
      "end_time": 428581.0,
      "text": "But I think the truth is the exact opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 428581.0,
      "end_time": 430832.0,
      "text": "I think citizens of high-tech societies"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 430832.0,
      "end_time": 434561.0,
      "text": "are more vulnerable to robotic weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434561.0,
      "end_time": 439250.0,
      "text": "and the reason can be summed up in one word: data."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 442507.0,
      "text": "Data powers high-tech societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 442507.0,
      "end_time": 445697.0,
      "text": "Cell phone geolocation, telecom metadata,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 445697.0,
      "end_time": 449169.0,
      "text": "social media, email, text, financial transaction data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 449169.0,
      "end_time": 452700.0,
      "text": "transportation data, it&#39;s a wealth of real-time data"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 452701.0,
      "end_time": 456740.0,
      "text": "on the movements and social interactions of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 456740.0,
      "end_time": 459849.0,
      "text": "In short, we are more visible to machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 459849.0,
      "end_time": 462910.0,
      "text": "than any people in history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 462910.0,
      "end_time": 467707.0,
      "text": "and this perfectly suits the targeting needs of autonomous weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 467707.0,
      "end_time": 469445.0,
      "text": "What you&#39;re looking at here"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 469445.0,
      "end_time": 472691.0,
      "text": "is a link analysis map of a social group."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 472691.0,
      "end_time": 476325.0,
      "text": "Lines indicate social connectedness between individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476325.0,
      "end_time": 479205.0,
      "text": "And these types of maps can be automatically generated"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 479205.0,
      "end_time": 483919.0,
      "text": "based on the data trail modern people leave behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 483920.0,
      "end_time": 486397.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s typically used to market goods and services"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 486397.0,
      "end_time": 490813.0,
      "text": "to targeted demographics, but it&#39;s a dual-use technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 490813.0,
      "end_time": 494173.0,
      "text": "because targeting is used in another context."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 494173.0,
      "end_time": 496733.0,
      "text": "Notice that certain individuals are highlighted."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 496733.0,
      "end_time": 500130.0,
      "text": "These are the hubs of social networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 500130.0,
      "end_time": 503602.0,
      "text": "These are organizers, opinion-makers, leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 503603.0,
      "end_time": 506285.0,
      "text": "and these people also can be automatically identified"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 506285.0,
      "end_time": 508667.0,
      "text": "from their communication patterns."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 508667.0,
      "end_time": 510813.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re a marketer, you might then target them"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 510813.0,
      "end_time": 513356.0,
      "text": "with product samples, try to spread your brand"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 513356.0,
      "end_time": 516184.0,
      "text": "through their social group."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 516183.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518136.99999999994,
      "text": "But if you&#39;re a repressive government"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 518138.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522948.00000000006,
      "text": "searching for political enemies, you might instead remove them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 522948.0,
      "end_time": 525708.0,
      "text": "eliminate them, disrupt their social group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 525708.0,
      "end_time": 528877.0,
      "text": "and those who remain behind lose social cohesion"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 528877.0,
      "end_time": 531497.0,
      "text": "and organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 531498.0,
      "end_time": 534822.0,
      "text": "Now in a world of cheap, proliferating robotic weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 534822.0,
      "end_time": 537457.0,
      "text": "borders would offer very little protection"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 537457.0,
      "end_time": 539403.0,
      "text": "to critics of distant governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 539403.0,
      "end_time": 543490.0,
      "text": "or trans-national criminal organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 543490.0,
      "end_time": 546542.0,
      "text": "Popular movements agitating for change"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 546542.0,
      "end_time": 550151.0,
      "text": "could be detected early and their leaders eliminated"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 550151.0,
      "end_time": 553610.0,
      "text": "before their ideas achieve critical mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 553620.0,
      "end_time": 555653.0,
      "text": "And ideas achieving critical mass"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 555653.0,
      "end_time": 559589.0,
      "text": "is what political activism in popular government is all about."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 559589.0,
      "end_time": 563586.0,
      "text": "Anonymous lethal weapons could make lethal action"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 563586.0,
      "end_time": 567368.0,
      "text": "an easy choice for all sorts of competing interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 567368.0,
      "end_time": 571102.0,
      "text": "And this would put a chill on free speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 571102.0,
      "end_time": 576410.0,
      "text": "and popular political action, the very heart of democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 576410.0,
      "end_time": 579324.0,
      "text": "And this is why we need an international treaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 579324.0,
      "end_time": 582863.0,
      "text": "on robotic weapons, and in particular a global ban"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 582864.0,
      "end_time": 586772.0,
      "text": "on the development and deployment of killer robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 586772.0,
      "end_time": 590260.0,
      "text": "Now we already have international treaties"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 590260.0,
      "end_time": 593411.0,
      "text": "on nuclear and biological weapons, and, while imperfect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 593412.0,
      "end_time": 595700.0,
      "text": "these have largely worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 595700.0,
      "end_time": 599468.0,
      "text": "But robotic weapons might be every bit as dangerous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 599468.0,
      "end_time": 602756.0,
      "text": "because they will almost certainly be used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 602756.0,
      "end_time": 607783.0,
      "text": "and they would also be corrosive to our democratic institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 607783.0,
      "end_time": 611251.0,
      "text": "Now in November 2012 the U.S. Department of Defense"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 611251.0,
      "end_time": 613709.0,
      "text": "issued a directive requiring"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 613709.0,
      "end_time": 618228.0,
      "text": "a human being be present in all lethal decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 618228.0,
      "end_time": 623300.0,
      "text": "This temporarily effectively banned autonomous weapons in the U.S. military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 623400.0,
      "end_time": 626757.0,
      "text": "but that directive needs to be made permanent."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 626757.0,
      "end_time": 631132.0,
      "text": "And it could set the stage for global action."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 631133.0,
      "end_time": 634978.0,
      "text": "Because we need an international legal framework"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 634978.0,
      "end_time": 637116.0,
      "text": "for robotic weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 637116.0,
      "end_time": 640440.0,
      "text": "And we need it now, before there&#39;s a devastating attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 640440.0,
      "end_time": 643196.0,
      "text": "or a terrorist incident that causes nations of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 643196.0,
      "end_time": 645120.0,
      "text": "to rush to adopt these weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 645120.0,
      "end_time": 648891.0,
      "text": "before thinking through the consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 648891.0,
      "end_time": 651872.0,
      "text": "Autonomous robotic weapons concentrate too much power"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 651872.0,
      "end_time": 658155.0,
      "text": "in too few hands, and they would imperil democracy itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 658155.0,
      "end_time": 660841.0,
      "text": "Now, don&#39;t get me wrong, I think there are tons"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 660841.0,
      "end_time": 663459.0,
      "text": "of great uses for unarmed civilian drones:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 663459.0,
      "end_time": 667397.0,
      "text": "environmental monitoring, search and rescue, logistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 667398.0,
      "end_time": 670224.0,
      "text": "If we have an international treaty on robotic weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 670224.0,
      "end_time": 673811.0,
      "text": "how do we gain the benefits of autonomous drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 673811.0,
      "end_time": 676459.0,
      "text": "and vehicles while still protecting ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 676459.0,
      "end_time": 680439.0,
      "text": "against illegal robotic weapons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 680439.0,
      "end_time": 685180.0,
      "text": "I think the secret will be transparency."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 685180.0,
      "end_time": 688193.0,
      "text": "No robot should have an expectation of privacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 688193.0,
      "end_time": 691644.0,
      "text": "in a public place."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 691644.0,
      "end_time": 696692.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 696692.0,
      "end_time": 698737.0,
      "text": "Each robot and drone should have"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 698737.0,
      "end_time": 701620.0,
      "text": "a cryptographically signed I.D. burned in at the factory"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 701620.0,
      "end_time": 704543.0,
      "text": "that can be used to track its movement through public spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 704543.0,
      "end_time": 707924.0,
      "text": "We have license plates on cars, tail numbers on aircraft."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 707924.0,
      "end_time": 709765.0,
      "text": "This is no different."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 709765.0,
      "end_time": 711776.0,
      "text": "And every citizen should be able to download an app"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 711777.0,
      "end_time": 714902.0,
      "text": "that shows the population of drones and autonomous vehicles"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 714902.0,
      "end_time": 717331.0,
      "text": "moving through public spaces around them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 717331.0,
      "end_time": 720640.0,
      "text": "both right now and historically."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 720640.0,
      "end_time": 723612.0,
      "text": "And civic leaders should deploy sensors and civic drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 723612.0,
      "end_time": 725956.0,
      "text": "to detect rogue drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 725956.0,
      "end_time": 729132.0,
      "text": "and instead of sending killer drones of their own up to shoot them down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 729132.0,
      "end_time": 732123.0,
      "text": "they should notify humans to their presence."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 732124.0,
      "end_time": 734730.0,
      "text": "And in certain very high-security areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 734730.0,
      "end_time": 736639.0,
      "text": "perhaps civic drones would snare them"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 736639.0,
      "end_time": 739480.0,
      "text": "and drag them off to a bomb disposal facility."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 739480.0,
      "end_time": 742507.0,
      "text": "But notice, this is more an immune system"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 742507.0,
      "end_time": 743828.0,
      "text": "than a weapons system."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 743828.0,
      "end_time": 746420.0,
      "text": "It would allow us to avail ourselves of the use"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 746420.0,
      "end_time": 748452.0,
      "text": "of autonomous vehicles and drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 748452.0,
      "end_time": 752747.0,
      "text": "while still preserving our open, civil society."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 752747.0,
      "end_time": 755746.0,
      "text": "We must ban the deployment and development"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 755746.0,
      "end_time": 757608.0,
      "text": "of killer robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 757608.0,
      "end_time": 762458.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s not succumb to the temptation to automate war."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 762458.0,
      "end_time": 765175.0,
      "text": "Autocratic governments and criminal organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 765176.0,
      "end_time": 768132.0,
      "text": "undoubtedly will, but let&#39;s not join them."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 768132.0,
      "end_time": 770220.0,
      "text": "Autonomous robotic weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 770230.0,
      "end_time": 772740.0,
      "text": "would concentrate too much power"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 772740.0,
      "end_time": 774555.0,
      "text": "in too few unseen hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 774556.0,
      "end_time": 777811.0,
      "text": "and that would be corrosive to representative government."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 777811.0,
      "end_time": 780772.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s make sure, for democracies at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 780772.0,
      "end_time": 783376.0,
      "text": "killer robots remain fiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 783376.0,
      "end_time": 784486.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 784486.0,
      "end_time": 789510.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 789510.0,
      "end_time": 793667.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}